## Overview

Five automated reports run on #b2b-cos. Four are powered by **Claude Cowork** (Anthropic's LLM agent platform) and post as Danny's Slack account. One is a standalone **Python/Databricks** job that posts via the **NuPay Update Bot**.

| Report | Cadence | Time (BRT) | Sender | Channel(s) |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| [Merchant Monitor](#1-b2b-merchant-monitor) | Weekdays | 09:30 | NuPay Update Bot | #b2b-cos |
| [Daily Digest](#2-b2b-daily-digest) | Weekdays | 19:00 | Danny (via Claude) | #b2b-cos |
| [Top of Mind](#3-b2b-top-of-mind) | Every Monday | 09:32 | Danny (via Claude) | #b2b-cos |
| [M-Team Update](#4-b2b-m-team-update) | 4th Monday/month | 09:35 | Danny (via Claude) | #b2b-cos + #b2b-announcements |
| [Feedback Review](#5-b2b-feedback-review) | Every Friday | 17:00 | Claude (private DM) | DM to Danny only |

